title: Canada : total university enrollment 2000 to 2018
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of students in thousands, containing a total of 19 data points.
Overall Number of students in thousands has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2009 and 2010.
The highest Number of students in thousands, of value 1341.35 was reached at Year 2018
Minimum Number of students in thousands about 846.6 was reached at Year 2000
